@host = http://localhost
@port = 3000
@url = {{host}}:{{port}}

@userToken = {{login.response.body.token}}
@adminToken = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Token megszerzése

# @name login
POST {{url}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teszt@example.com",
  "password": "jelszo123"
}

### Összes order item lekérése (admin)
GET {{url}}/api/order-items
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### egy order item darabszámának lekérése (admin)
GET {{url}}/api/order-items/oi-0002/quantity
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Order itemek lekérése order_id alapján
GET {{url}}/api/order-items/order/22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Új order item létrehozása
POST {{url}}/api/order-items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "order_id": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "product_id": "d40880ea-359d-11f1-b4fd-581122d0f62d",
  "quantity": 2,
  "price": 1999.99
}


### Order item frissítése
PATCH {{url}}/api/order-items/bbbb1111-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "quantity": 5
}

### Order item törlése (admin)
DELETE {{url}}/api/order-items/aaaa2222-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}